document_data.name: Dartwell
document_data.mainbody: '''Dartwell''' was a [[half-elf]] market grifter in [[Waterdeep]] in the 1470s [[DR]].
document_data.History:
In [[1476 DR]], Dartwell entered into [[Undermountain]] after fleeing from the [[City Watch (Waterdeep)|City Watch]] after swindling some merchants. Feeling weary, he decided to sit for a moment in the [[Hall of Sleeping Kings]], and stayed asleep

He may have been awoken in [[1479 DR]].
